---
layout: base.njk
title: Trainings
description: Hands-on workshops for engineering teams.
permalink: /trainings/index.html
---
<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
  <div class="mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-stone-900 mb-4">Trainings</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-stone-500 max-w-2xl">Hands-on workshops for engineering teams on platform engineering, TypeScript, and developer experience.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
    {%- for training in collections.training | reverse -%}
    <article class="group bg-white rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 hover:border-amber-300 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-200 overflow-hidden hover:-translate-y-0.5">
      <div class="bg-stone-900 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white leading-snug group-hover:text-stone-200 transition-colors">
          <a href="{{ training.url }}">{{ training.data.title }}</a>
        </h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-3">
          <span class="text-xs font-medium text-stone-300 bg-stone-700 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">⏱ {{ training.data.duration }}</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-medium text-stone-300 bg-stone-700 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">👥 {{ training.data.audience | truncate(30) }}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6">
        <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">{{ training.data.description }}</p>
        <a href="{{ training.url }}" class="inline-flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-amber-700 hover:text-amber-800 transition-colors gap-1">
          View curriculum →
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="bg-stone-900 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to upskill your team?</h2>
    <p class="text-stone-400 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">All workshops are available in-person or virtually and can be customised for your team&rsquo;s needs.</p>
    <a href="/about/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full transition-colors shadow-lg">
      Get in touch
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
